<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٨١:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: <span class="c3">{الفَلَقُ}</span>: الصُّبْحُ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> أَبْيَنُ مِنْ فَرَقِ وَفَلَقِ الصُّبْحِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{غَاسِقٍ}</span>: اللَّيْلُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{إِذَا وَقَبَ}</span>: غُرُوبُ الشَّمْسِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ويُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَقَبَ}</span>: إِذَا دَخَلَ فِي كُلِّ شَيْءٍ وَأَظْلَمَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٧ص١٣٦:</span> <span class="c3">{النَّفَّاثَاتُ}</span>: السَّوَاحِرُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>